Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The plane we're gonna be riding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Boeing 747.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a jumbo jet, 70.7 meters long!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri, private eye, babysitting brats on a trip to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure have some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who went all "Wait for me, my cute seaside angels" last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was before I knew I had to babysit a bunch of brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason we're even here is because\NDr. Agasa won this trip on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful that you can come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how come I can't see our lucky doctor yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doc's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just called him. He told me he came\Ndown with a cold and can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though he asked for lots of souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's going to pass as well\Nto look after the doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's buy her a lot of souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, the houses keep getting smaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was up all night reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just remembering the flight I took last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, Shin'ichi also fell\Nasleep right after we took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and that detective kid ran off to LA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I was away on a trip that I won at the neighborhood drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just went to visit his parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, teenage kids don't go on {\i1}overseas{\i0} trips together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, his parents were the ones who sent me the ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, back then, he didn't try anything... {\i1}funny{\i0}, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "funny"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How do I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sit down, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ya talkin' to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you put out that cigarette?\NThis is a non-smoking section.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsuneo Ukai (47)\NExecutive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You're causing trouble\Nfor the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you want to smoke,\Nthere's an area in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.80,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro Ōtaka (29)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll try to be more {\i1}thoughtful{\i0} next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.64,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi Amano (27)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please knock it off, Kazuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are ya seriously scolding your boyfriend who's gonna be stinkin' rich soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lighten up some!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That American newspaper said they'll give me a whole lotta green for these negatives, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If{\i0} those negatives are the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:41.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I don't know if those actually are scandalous shots of a powerful American senator or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:40.21,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Chizuru Tachikawa (29)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you've got the wrong man,\Nthis'll just be a bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already faxed 'em two of the shots to confirm it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine and all, but just don't\Nforget that we're on vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This deal with your shots comes second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait 'til ya get a load of our surfing skills.{it's "our" skills, cuz of the "ore-tachi" here, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Saginuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:11.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Noboru Saginuma (30)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's with him? He's already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I'll catch a nap too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:23.17,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Edward Crowe (51)\NFreelance Journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I help you, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling airsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any airsickness pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. Just a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir. May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:07:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm not too fond of planes.\NI just feel uncomfortable sitting still.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Could you do me a little favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sick. The stewardess went to get me some medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you take the airsick pills I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd. They seem to be\Nworking fine on Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to switch seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sitting by the window might make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's the one who needed the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are. The medicine and some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got up a while ago and went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's also feeling sick and went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been knocking on the door,\Nbut the guy inside won't answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir? Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it came from the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I have your attention, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a passenger who has fallen ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there is a doctor or nurse on board,\Nplease report to your nearest flight attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Megure from the MPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there really a sick person aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone {\i1}died{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's in the toilet in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, where did he wander off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? If it isn't Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Off on vacation during the school break?{vs. Off on vacation during the long weekend?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I heard that somebody {\i1}died{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Just leave everything to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody has disturbed the scene, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, some strange boy did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was most likely\Nsuffocation by damage to the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is a pointed object, similar to an ice pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:10:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim may have already been unconscious from inhaling some kind of chemical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough information for that yet.{pre-gonbe-edit:That's what I don't know yet.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer is still in this big tin can\Nthat's flying above the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let that person get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was the first page in his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi Kudo, detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This was Shin'ichi's first case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kudo? Are you Yusaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're his son, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the spitting image of your dad in the old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you since\Nyou were in the sixth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But man, you've grown so tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you've got no business here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still in high school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just meddle with a crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Could you borrow a camera from someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to take pictures of the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you need pictures,\Nthat boy already took some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About sixty, I believe. I borrowed the camera from a passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told us to keep an eye on his actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he didn't do anything suspicious, like trying to hide something or wipe something off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you move the body, you'll destroy the stiffening of the muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making it harder to determine\Nthe estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the livor mortis and the\Nfact that his chin was already stiffening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say he's been dead for an hour or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are three things that struck me as being just plain odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, even though there were spots of\Nblood on the wall where the body was leaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there wasn't any blood on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secondly, there's a strange scratch at\Nthe lower right of the fatal wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And last but not least, the inside of his\Ntrousers' left pocket was soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though his hands were completely dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if you shove a wet hand into your pocket, it wouldn't get that wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that somebody\Nmust've soaked it for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Argh! Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to leave this to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but could you get the man sleeping in the seat next to mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's also a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "detective"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just a regular high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let me get near the body otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've told me where you were going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried sick about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you were sleeping so peacefully with that dopey look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by dopey look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're late, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was most likely\Nsuffocation by damage to the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is a pointed object, similar to an ice pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the livor mortis and rigor mortis, he died one or two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? There's an empty bottle and a handkerchief in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the killer soaked the handkerchief in something like chloroform, carried it around in a bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and knocked the victim out with it before killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. We'd like to store the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I have a plastic bag or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that everything you just said has been exactly the same as what that boy said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were astonished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That boy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look. The one over there with the black pullover.{sweater in en_US, jumper in en_GB, we decided to use pullover to avoid en_US AND any confusement}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His dad's a mystery writer who used to help me whenever I couldn't figure out a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he was still little, his dad used to bring him along to crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never would've thought he'd pick up detection skills like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds pretty neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An amateur's still an amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just a teenager who got big ideas from\Nreading too many mysteries and medical books!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's look for potential witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with four suspects here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only four people, apart from the victim, went to the toilet at the key time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My seat's at the very end of the row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had my eyes open the whole night, and\Nnobody went to the smoking area behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had your eyes open?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were awake all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I couldn't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you fall asleep the\Nmoment you got on the plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy! Falling asleep early and then waking up in the middle of the night, just like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:41.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You really expected me to fall asleep with you right next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not that mature yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then could you identify\Nthose four people for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the four people were...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the woman next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the man sitting across the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the foreigner in the seat in front is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all seated close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did this happen to Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what we're trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those negatives could be a motive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Negatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him showing them off to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He claimed he'd earn big money by selling them to some newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he didn't have any on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the murderer must be someone who was aware of those negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anybody in our business would've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He offered to sell them to plenty of newspapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ōtaka was stabbed in the back of the head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the killer must've been a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two are just photographers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a bit off base to suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it could've been done by anyone with an anaesthetic weapon and basic medical knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, even a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for now, let's hear you all\Nout about your trips to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the toilet because I wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm certain that Kazuhiro was still there when I got back to my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, I asked the stewardess to bring me some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why I still remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He still seemed to be asleep, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw that from down the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It indeed looked as if she was asking for some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the toilet right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I was there for about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Down the aisle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't your seat across from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was walking around since I don't like sitting for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when did the victim leave his seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I brought her the medicine\Nand water, he had already left his seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm fairly certain that I got back in less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the bathroom about twenty\Nminutes after Tsugumi got her medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to see how Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was doing\Nbecause he had been away for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he was still alive then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:19:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, when I knocked on this door and asked whether he was doing fine, he knocked back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know\Nwhich one he was in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked all the other ones\Nand they were all unoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,When did you go to the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember when I did, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says he doesn't remember when he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That foreigner uses a really strong cologne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! How many more useless questions will you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoever has the murder weapon must be the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be faster to just perform a body check on those four and check their luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since I never went to the toilet and was asleep the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also left your seat, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your seat's right behind the victim's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember how I said the victim was still\Nasleep in his seat before I went to the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear that he wasn't there at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's just crazy talk, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only you and the other three went to the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he testified!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:29.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, I {\i1}was{\i0}\Ndistracted for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, I must ask all five of you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to get body-checked in the lavatory and have your baggage searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't find a weapon on them or in their bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, nobody had anything\Nsimilar to an ice pick on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have also searched all\Npossible spots on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nothing was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:21:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure they were the only ones who went to the lavatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the murder weapon couldn't be found, then that must mean
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that the murderer is probably still carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that must be the culprit's trump card.{very probably not a thought, though who knows...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And I'll find that trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:32.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Before this iron bird rests its wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want us to do a full search of the five suspects and their belongings once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we can't find the\Nweapon on board the plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the murderer might still be\Ncarrying it, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.82,0:22:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First up, Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, purse{en_gb;was wallet}, handkerchief,\Nmakeup kit, tissues, boarding pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a pair of sunglasses, camera,\Nnotebook, and a ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think any of this could be a potential murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that ballpoint pen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you look inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up is Amano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, wallet, handkerchief,\Nknit hat, boarding pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,camera, makeup kit, sewing kit and some medicine for airsickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only edged tools here are the small\Nscissors and needle in the sewing kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like a far stretch to think someone could kill with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up is Ukai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, boarding pass, wallet, handkerchief,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,electric razor, towel and some shaving cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Next up is Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us check your belongings, just in case.{it's probably either "Let us..." or "Well, let's..."<GonbeFAN> might be "Will I" too\N<GonbeFAN> probably "Let us" though\N<GonbeFAN> or maybe "We'll"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it appears you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:27.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:31.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The cologne is the most strong around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:33.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe he has none on his wrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, wallet, handkerchief, boarding pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,towel, newspaper, two paperback books, glasses case, sewing kit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a checkbook from the\NAmerican National Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this checkbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Edward, I'd like to ask you a few questions\Nabout the checkbook in your briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's for my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was to buy some art object\Nat the auction in Japan.{art or foreign object? probably art, though}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nothing caught my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He intended to buy an art\Nobject at an auction in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he couldn't find anything to his interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.54,0:24:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the last one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.08,0:24:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, wallet, handkerchief, camera, some negatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.96,0:24:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wristwatch, cigarettes, lighter, boarding pass and medicine for airsickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot of medicine you've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.39,0:24:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I easily get airsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.77,0:24:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru and Tsugumi lent me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.14,0:24:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.89,0:24:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.02,0:24:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I look at those negatives real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.40,0:24:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.99,0:24:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in these photographs...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.32,0:24:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the American senator Dickson{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.29,0:25:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.66,0:25:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's with a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.29,0:25:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's enough, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.58,0:25:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.54,0:25:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds just like Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.67,0:25:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just like his? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.01,0:25:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here they are in your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.59,0:25:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.22,0:25:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-These are {\i1}my{\i0} negatives!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at that hotel with Ōtaka, taking the same pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.73,0:25:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ōtaka's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ōtaka's were better than mine.\NMine weren't so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.36,0:25:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was gonna try sell 'em anyway to some newspaper office in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you want to blame the murder\Non me, then go find the weapon first!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.58,0:25:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now. I'll be happy\Nto talk after the body check.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.71,0:25:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'd like everyone to enter\Nthe toilet, one at a time, as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.46,0:25:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stewardess will be checking the woman,\Nwhile the men will be checked by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.88,0:25:58.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So this is Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.68,0:26:01.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}According to the seat numbers on the boarding passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.97,0:26:05.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was behind him,\Nand in front of him sat Edward{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.77,0:26:09.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Amano{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} sat to his right, and next to her was Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.31,0:26:12.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And across the aisle to his left sat Ukai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th—
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.24,0:26:22.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a fragment of a film negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.41,0:26:25.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's it doing in the seat\Nnext to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.71,0:26:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.71,0:26:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They just finished the body check.{Viz: The body check's finished, but they haven't found a weapon!}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.38,0:26:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like nobody had a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.38,0:26:37.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means the only place left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.88,0:26:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see now? We didn't have any weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.35,0:26:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to strip buck naked {\i1}twice{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.56,0:26:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.31,0:26:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do, Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.36,0:26:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've searched every possible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.44,0:26:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's still one more place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.28,0:26:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a place we haven't searched yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.32,0:27:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The luggage of the victim, Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one belongs to Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.55,0:27:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.34,0:27:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one behind that black bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.35,0:27:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something unusual he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.31,0:27:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something unusual...?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.48,0:27:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A week ago, he forgot his bag in the studio, and somebody tore it to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.99,0:27:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he had to buy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.20,0:27:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...a new one for this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody thought the\Nnegatives might've been inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.04,0:28:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, camera, film, a pair of\Nsunglasses, three packs of cigarettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.47,0:28:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wallet, towel, two magazines,\Nboarding pass, and wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.47,0:28:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing like this looks like\Nthe murder weapon to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.31,0:28:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.35,0:28:13.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.94,0:28:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.44,0:28:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kazuhiro Ōtaka".
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.61,0:28:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who won the {\i1}Nichiuri Shimbun{\i0} Photo Awards three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.99,0:28:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.95,0:28:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same Kazuhiro Ōtaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.00,0:28:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.29,0:28:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.62,0:28:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.04,0:28:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That photograph of a mother caught in a fire handing her baby to a fireman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.43,0:28:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.34,0:28:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that currently matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.22,0:28:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are we cleared of the charges now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.22,0:28:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or not? Well, which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.68,0:28:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But you people were the only ones who went\Nto the toilet around the time of the murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.19,0:28:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...according to this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.82,0:29:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet the young detective simply fell asleep and missed a couple of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.62,0:29:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly seems like you've read lots of books and did lots of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.75,0:29:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.71,0:29:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not some fictional story.{BuriBot, j-ball shousetsu 3! (J-Ball) 小説 [しょうせつ] /(n,adj-no) novel/(short) story/(P)/}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.17,0:29:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Children should behave and just go back to their seat, and take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.67,0:29:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.13,0:29:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna stand up to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.26,0:29:25.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.89,0:29:28.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We can't find the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.97,0:29:31.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And their stories just don't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.52,0:29:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's about time to confess already?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.90,0:29:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.69,0:29:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the murderer, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.11,0:29:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.28,0:29:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's pretty obvious that you're\Nthe only one among us who's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.32,0:29:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.24,0:29:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When this lady asked for some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.95,0:29:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You claimed you were in your\Nseat back then, but that's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.42,0:29:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.50,0:29:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's not nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.50,0:30:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that... back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.30,0:30:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That stewardess...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.92,0:30:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She also must've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.26,0:30:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or so he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.47,0:30:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.39,0:30:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.89,0:30:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gentleman was wandering\Naround the cabin, so I stopped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.94,0:30:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then complained about someone who\Nwas smoking in the non-smoking section.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.32,0:30:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was this person in his seat back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.41,0:30:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.83,0:30:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.21,0:30:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on! What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.42,0:30:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the one who brought the medicine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.17,0:30:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.67,0:30:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You saw me asleep in my seat, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.18,0:30:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.72,0:30:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.06,0:30:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.68,0:30:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.81,0:30:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that when you brought the medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.98,0:31:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.90,0:31:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes, you're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.15,0:31:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I was just imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.49,0:31:09.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.78,0:31:12.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.03,0:31:13.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.62,0:31:17.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All testimonies except the killer's...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.58,0:31:20.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The negative fragement in the seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:24.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The unusual bloodstain in the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:26.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And why the victim's pockets were wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.71,0:31:28.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It all fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.43,0:31:30.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.47,0:31:34.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why did we not find the weapon on the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.56,0:31:36.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.85,0:31:38.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That it couldn't be thrown away?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.73,0:31:41.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something that'd lead us\Nimmediately to that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.65,0:31:45.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.78,0:31:47.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Back then that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.61,0:31:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.45,0:31:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure is looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.20,0:31:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to ask you whether or not you remember anyone else who went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.12,0:31:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, more importantly, Ran, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.21,0:32:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...in high school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.62,0:32:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.50,0:32:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, lemme ask you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.51,0:32:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wh-Wha-Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.34,0:32:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer already!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.97,0:32:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing for me too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.18,0:32:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.47,0:32:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most of them are like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.44,0:32:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.48,0:32:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.73,0:32:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just what do you mean by "I see"?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.86,0:32:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've finally figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.03,0:32:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trump card that the killer used to finish off the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.08,0:32:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.25,0:32:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one of you who has\Nmade any suspicious moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.58,0:32:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is you, Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.17,0:32:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.84,0:32:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.67,0:32:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is not the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.22,0:33:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man never went near the crime scene,\Nso there's a 0% chance that he's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.02,0:33:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.06,0:33:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.81,0:33:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you I wasn't involved with any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.32,0:33:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.28,0:33:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} involved in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.95,0:33:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.62,0:33:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were being used by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.29,0:33:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By one of those four people who isn't telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.58,0:33:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.04,0:33:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.00,0:33:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who claims to have gone to the toilet to check on the victim, knocked on the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.84,0:33:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that then someone knocked back was Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.38,0:33:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.97,0:33:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.55,0:33:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.26,0:33:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.68,0:33:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There really was someone inside the toilet room...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.27,0:33:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.23,0:33:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, that was you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.44,0:33:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.36,0:33:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While looking for the negatives he put his hand inside Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.57,0:34:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and realized that some of the cologne from his wrists got on the victim's trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.75,0:34:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he quickly washed the cologne off his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.75,0:34:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and wiped that distinctive scent out of the pocket with a wet handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.80,0:34:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him not having any cologne on his wrists is the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.39,0:34:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't really classify as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.68,0:34:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the questioning would have to be done in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.52,0:34:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he can actually speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.27,0:34:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.98,0:34:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.49,0:34:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.07,0:34:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.24,0:34:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...in Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.41,0:34:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.91,0:34:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to buy those negatives with that National Bank check.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.08,0:34:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.42,0:34:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.17,0:34:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senator Dickson, the man in those\Nscandalous photos, requested me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.63,0:34:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the one who killed Ōtaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.38,0:35:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.47,0:35:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when he entered the toilet, Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was already a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.14,0:35:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.44,0:35:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.19,0:35:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, when I heard that he went to the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.57,0:35:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I realized that it was my opportunity to make a deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.32,0:35:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I got no reply after knocking on the door, I forced myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.70,0:35:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there he was... Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.71,0:35:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't get my hands on the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.17,0:35:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the one who knocked back were...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.09,0:35:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.67,0:35:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.59,0:35:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just playing along with the kid's guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.89,0:35:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.72,0:35:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.43,0:35:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was blood on the toilet's wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.02,0:35:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't any on the victim's back\Neven though that he was leaning there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.48,0:36:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That indicates that someone else\Nmust've moved the body later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.95,0:36:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who found the body without notifying anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.28,0:36:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only reason I could think of to move the body would be to look for the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.50,0:36:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unable to find it, he searched inside the victim's pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.80,0:36:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only person who would do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.55,0:36:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,must have been someone who couldn't see what the victim was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person would be Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.10,0:36:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.85,0:36:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, who's the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.56,0:36:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have now ruled out Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and the\None who knocked on the door, Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.06,0:36:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that Ukai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and\NAmano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} are the only suspects left.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.36,0:36:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's an important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.49,0:36:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Amano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked a\Nstewardess for some medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.28,0:36:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there was nobody sitting in Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nseat —\hthe one behind the victim's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.91,0:36:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what Ukai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.75,0:36:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.42,0:36:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I kept telling you that I was asleep in my seat the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.75,0:37:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nsleeping in his seat the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.68,0:37:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the killer put a knit hat and an eye mask on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.27,0:37:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, doesn't that match...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.23,0:37:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it matches what\NŌtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wore while sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.94,0:37:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After killing Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, instead of returning to their own seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.65,0:37:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the killer sat next to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} while being\Ndressed like Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and called the stewardess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.95,0:37:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way it'd seem like Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still alive at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.87,0:37:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.46,0:37:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.08,0:37:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and used Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to create a fake alibi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.18,0:37:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi Amano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.98,0:37:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.65,0:37:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.65,0:38:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't blame the stewardess\Nfor her mistake, because it was so dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.07,0:38:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and most of his face was covered up.{*UTB: & the only part of his not covered by the blanket, was the nose up... Viz: and she couldn't see much of the person under the blanket.UTB seems more literal, but is weirdly worded, please reTL}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.16,0:38:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went back to her own seat when the stewardess was getting the medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.41,0:38:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and woke up Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} by coughing loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.76,0:38:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All to make her notice that Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't in his seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.09,0:38:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus making Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the stewardess think that Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.31,0:38:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-In that case, the empty seat I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.60,0:38:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've seen the empty seat behind Sazanuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.61,0:38:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she wouldn't be able to pull off that trick if the\Nseat next to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was to be occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.45,0:38:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she ordered an extra ticket without\Ncancelling it, the seat {\i1}would{\i0} remain empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.66,0:38:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she gave Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sleeping pills instead\Nof airsick pills, then he wouldn't wake up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.50,0:39:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a knit hat in her luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.13,0:39:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she was aware of Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s habit of wearing an eye mask when sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.39,0:39:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if the stewardess noticed Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't sitting next to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.14,0:39:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that can easily be camouflaged by putting a blanket over your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.98,0:39:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The negatives were cut to pieces with the sewing kit's scissors and flushed down the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.99,0:39:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All to make it look like that the killer was after the negatives
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.32,0:39:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to draw away attention from her and her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.29,0:39:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a piece of the negative on the seat next to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.41,0:39:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which must've stuck to her\Nclothes and fell down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.00,0:39:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.13,0:39:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.84,0:39:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what must have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.46,0:39:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She waited until Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.43,0:39:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and told Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that she wanted to talk and told him to wait in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.60,0:39:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She then took her drugged handkerchief in\Na bottle and weapon, and went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.06,0:40:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after opening the door, she pressed the handkerchief into his face to knock him out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.65,0:40:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stabbed him in the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now she had to cut up and flush away the negatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.65,0:40:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lock the door from the outside, and set up her trick so that it seems Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} still was alive
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.08,0:40:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when she returned from the toilet.\NHer alibi was now established.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.67,0:40:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if someone going to the toilet saw her leaving the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.46,0:40:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that she left the door unlocked during the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.93,0:40:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So even if someone wanted to use the toilet,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.18,0:40:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she could easily keep the door closed because of it being so narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.65,0:40:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person outside would realize that it's occupied and just go to another toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.44,0:40:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.28,0:40:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to accuse Tsugumi then you better show us some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.78,0:40:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.41,0:40:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the weapon and proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.91,0:40:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, she still has it on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.04,0:41:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you blabbering about? You forgot that she went through two body checks?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.67,0:41:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something that can bypass a search.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It also can get past metal detectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.68,0:41:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only women have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.55,0:41:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Only women have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.56,0:41:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if something that convenient exists, you silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.23,0:41:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me, Tsugumi, that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.44,0:41:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I'm talking about, Tsugumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.78,0:41:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the metal wire in the right\Nside of the bra you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.20,0:41:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for a woman to\Nkill someone with such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.79,0:41:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, if you sharpen one edge and stab the back of the neck with full power,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.46,0:41:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and penetrate about 5 to 6 centimeters, it'll reach the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.51,0:41:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.26,0:41:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a peculiar scratch mark left near the fatal injury on his neck. That's the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.93,0:42:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've been left there when the other end of the wire scratched the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.60,0:42:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't get rid of the weapon because if it'd be discovered at the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.61,0:42:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'd figure out that the woman with\Na missing wire in her bra would be the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.28,0:42:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! Let's just have her go\Nthrough one more body check.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.25,0:42:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't, Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.67,0:42:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because then they'd find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.38,0:42:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.88,0:42:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.22,0:42:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed Kazuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.35,0:42:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the photo that made him win the\N{\i1}Nichiuri Shimbun{\i0} Photo Award three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.48,0:42:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying? Wasn't that photo what brought you two together?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.44,0:42:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. He caught my interest because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.24,0:43:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was amazed that someone was able to capture the horror of the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.91,0:43:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that took my brother's life, on film.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.12,0:43:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the only photo he took.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.59,0:43:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found dozens of photos in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.67,0:43:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some from when the smoke started to rise from the flat building,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.18,0:43:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even panoramic shots from before the fire even started!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.97,0:43:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.73,0:43:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...start that fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.15,0:43:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! He even boasted about it when I confronted him with the photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.19,0:43:39.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You don't wait for perfect\Nmoments. You {\i1}make{\i0} them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.49,0:43:40.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.37,0:43:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.58,0:43:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.42,0:43:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was confident in where I hid the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.05,0:43:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You raised your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.92,0:44:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were about to get his bag from the luggage rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.76,0:44:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your right arm stopped and then you used your left arm instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.52,0:44:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gave you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.27,0:44:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sharpened edge of the wire must've\Npricked you, which is what made you stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.19,0:44:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-From that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.69,0:44:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From {\i1}just{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.78,0:44:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has long been an axiom of mine that the little things are infinitely the most important.{IMPORTANT - he might possibly not be quoting Holmes word-for-word}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.29,0:44:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That little gesture you made just struck me as odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.46,0:44:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her arm... Did you notice it, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.68,0:44:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.27,0:44:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.60,0:44:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you going to LA?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.90,0:44:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to pick up a Japanese criminal who's on the international list from the LAPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.90,0:44:58.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:01.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.24,0:45:03.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why he asked me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.96,0:46:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.71,0:46:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Could you show me your bra?"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.00,0:46:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"There's a wire in it, isn't there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.80,0:46:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who asks a woman such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.26,0:46:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you know that's\Nsexual harassment, Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.14,0:46:49.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.47,0:46:52.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me Ran's dreaming about {\i1}that{\i0} case.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.18,0:46:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.23,0:46:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That creep {\i1}did{\i0} try something, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.65,0:47:00.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.65,0:47:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's she dreaming about.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.44,0:47:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dreamed about stuffing myself with eel on rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.99,0:47:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, we're about to land. Please return to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.20,0:47:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot! How can I stay calm when my daughter's virtue is endangered!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.33,0:47:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.71,0:47:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.71,0:47:19.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,sekuhara
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.83,0:47:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta mean a dessert stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.83,0:47:21.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,betsubara
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.73,0:47:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.62,0:47:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.88,0:47:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The less I understand of it, the more it goes wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.62,0:47:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My uncontrollable curiosity!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.74,0:47:56.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Secret of the Moon, Star and Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.74,0:47:56.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,(Part I)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.74,0:47:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: The Secret of the Moon, Star and Sun (Part I).
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.75,0:48:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: ¥1 coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.71,0:48:07.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.71,0:48:03.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The next episode is on the 11th of October!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.34,0:48:07.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran, when're you gonna\Ndream about me again?
